items.title: First Tip:
items.guide1: You have to lick only the good food, like cakes and chicken...

items.title: Second Tip:
items.guide1: You need to avoid things that are not good for humans. like mushroom and poo.

items.title: Third Tip:
items.guide1: Try to collect as many points as you can by only licking the good food.

items.title: Fourth Tip:
items.guide1: Keep licking until the green progress bar in the top is full.

items.title: Fifth Tip:
items.guide1: Bad Food will make you lose points the and the game.
